Package oogasalad.editor.model.data.object.event

Class EditorEvent

java.lang.Object
oogasalad.editor.model.data.object.event.EditorEvent
public class EditorEvent extends Object
Represents an event associated with an editor object, encapsulating its conditions, outcomes, and corresponding parameter mappings.
Author:
Jacob You
